<name>BRAKE</name>
<section id="1002J_S0010" variety="S0010">
<name>BRAKE CONTROL</name>
<ttl id="1002J_S0010_72W30_T005W" variety="T005W">
<name>VEHICLE STABILITY CONTROL SYSTEM (for BOSCH Made)</name>
<para id="RM000000YHJ009X" category="J" type-id="305SV" name-id="BC1HJ-01" from="200601">
<dtccode/>
<dtcname>Slip Indicator Light does not Come ON</dtcname>
<subpara id="RM000000YHJ009X_01" type-id="60" category="03" proc-id="RM0250U___00003OD00000">
<name>DESCRIPTION</name>
<content5 releasenbr="1">
<ptxt>The skid control ECU is connected to the combination meter assembly via CAN communication.</ptxt>
<ptxt>The SLIP indicator light blinks during VSC and/or TRAC operation.</ptxt>
<ptxt>When the system fails, the SLIP indicator light comes on to warn the driver (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM000001NK3001X"/>).</ptxt>
</content5>
</subpara>
<subpara id="RM000000YHJ009X_02" type-id="32" category="03" proc-id="RM0250U___00003OE00000">
<name>WIRING DIAGRAM</name>
<content5 releasenbr="1">
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C136510E05" width="7.106578999in" height="8.799559038in"/>
</figure>
</content5>
</subpara>
<subpara id="RM000000YHJ009X_03" type-id="51" category="05" proc-id="RM0250U___00003OF00000">
<name>INSPECTION PROCEDURE</name>
<content5 releasenbr="1">
<atten4>
<ptxt>Check the condition of each related circuit connector before troubleshooting (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM000000UZ301TX"/>).</ptxt>
</atten4>
</content5>
</subpara>
<subpara id="RM000000YHJ009X_04" type-id="01" category="01">
<name>PROCEDURE</name>
<testgrp id="RM000000YHJ009X_04_0001" proc-id="RM0250U___00003OG00000">
<testtitle>CHECK CAN COMMUNICATION SYSTEM</testtitle>
<content6 releasenbr="1">
<test1>
<ptxt>Check if a CAN communication system DTC is output (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM000001NK5001X"/>).</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Result</title>
<table pgwide="1">
<tgroup cols="2">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="4.54in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="2.54in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>CAN communication system DTC is not output</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>A</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>CAN communication system DTC is output</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>B</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
</test1>
</content6>
<res>
<down ref="RM000000YHJ009X_04_0003" fin="false">A</down>
<right ref="RM000000YHJ009X_04_0006" fin="true">B</right>
</res>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM000000YHJ009X_04_0003" proc-id="RM0250U___00003OI00000">
<testtitle>INSPECT COMBINATION METER ASSEMBLY</testtitle>
<content6 releasenbr="1">
<test1>
<ptxt>Connect the intelligent tester to the DLC3.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Perform "ACTIVE TEST" of the combination meter assembly using the intelligent tester (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM0000012G700DX"/>).</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Check the SLIP indicator light operation.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>OK</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>The SLIP indicator light turns on or off in accordance with the intelligent tester.</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
</test1>
</content6>
<res>
<down ref="RM000000YHJ009X_04_0008" fin="true">OK</down>
<right ref="RM000000YHJ009X_04_0009" fin="true">NG</right>
</res>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM000000YHJ009X_04_0006">
<testtitle>INSPECT CAN COMMUNICATION SYSTEM<xref label="Seep01" href="RM000000WI600QX"/>
</testtitle>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM000000YHJ009X_04_0008">
<testtitle>REPLACE BRAKE ACTUATOR ASSEMBLY<xref label="Seep01" href="RM0000013P6004X"/>
</testtitle>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM000000YHJ009X_04_0009">
<testtitle>REPLACE COMBINATION METER ASSEMBLY<xref label="Seep01" href="RM0000024D7000X"/>
</testtitle>
</testgrp>
</subpara>
</para>
</ttl>
